{"type":"message","id":"f971351c","parentId":"80b4739f","timestamp":"2026-04-04T06:24:25.493Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both ports are responding:\n- Port 1933 returns a JSON `{\"detail\":\"Not Found\"}` - this means the API is running and responding (404 on root, which is expected)\n- Port 8020 returns the OpenViking Console HTML page\n\nSo OpenViking is running and accessible. Let me report this back to the user.","thinkingSignature":"453cd7e5396b54eb76e12f51a9430b124bcddd06677d4cfedb864f53b357375d"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] OpenViking 数据库运行正常，可以联通：\n\n| 端口 | 服务 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **1933** | OpenViking API | ✅ 正常（返回 404 是预期的，根路径无内容） |\n| **8020** | OpenViking Console | ✅ 正常（Dashboard 可访问） |\n\nDocker 容器 IP 是 `172.17.0.2`，主服务监听 1933，控制台在 8020。\n\n有什么具体要测试的功能吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2312,"output":186,"cacheRead":12515,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15013,"cost":{"input":0.0006935999999999999,"output":0.00022319999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0007509,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0016676999999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775283859713,"responseId":"061fe194ea9f4049a0225e524b2b81fc"}}
