{"type":"message","id":"78425b21","parentId":"c74b0e78","timestamp":"2026-04-04T10:36:44.974Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the full picture. The clawhub.ai website itself loads, but the API at `/api/v1/skills` returns empty items. This could be a network issue from China to the clawhub.ai servers, or the API is actually returning empty.\n\nThe HTML page shows \"No highlighted skills yet\" and \"No popular skills yet\" - this might actually be a real empty state on the registry, or there's a network connectivity problem from China.\n\nLet me check if there's actually any China mirror or if the user was just asking in general. The user said \"在看一下\" which implies they want me to look more carefully. Maybe they expected me to find a China-specific mirror URL.\n\n\nI'm noticing the page displays \"No skills yet. Be the first.\" which appears to be a genuinely empty state rather than a network issue, but the user is specifically asking about whether ClawHub has switched to a China source—suggesting they believe there's something to find here that I'm missing.","thinkingSignature":"89772092d129a69feb5d3a61350aaf9998b3b1ec12fba29c5055434d5ab12af0"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 检查完了，如实说：\n\n**网站** `https://clawhub.ai` — 能访问，正常打开\n**API** `/api/v1/skills` — 返回空列表（`{\"items\":[]}`）\n**clawhub explore** — 也显示 \"No skills found\"\n\n网站首页显示 \"No highlighted skills yet\" 和 \"No popular skills yet\"，看起来 registry 确实是空的，不是网络问题。\n\n**没有检测到任何中国源切换：**\n- 无 npmmirror / 腾讯云 / 阿里云镜像配置\n- `clawhub config` 里 registry 仍是 `https://clawhub.ai`\n- 环境变量里也没有镜像相关配置\n\n你是想从国内访问更快，还是听到风声说 clawhub 要出国内版？我可以帮你盯着这事。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":10197,"output":364,"cacheRead":12515,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23076,"cost":{"input":0.0030591,"output":0.0004368,"cacheRead":0.0007509,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004246799999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775298985798,"responseId":"06201caad83264026617abee854c5111"}}
